      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Rack Inventory\n\nTrack every device in your data center racks with device type icons, monitoring status coloring, and one-click access to management interfaces.\n\n### Features demonstrated\n\n- 🔀 **Device type icons** — type strings mapped to emojis via value mappings\n- 🟢 **Monitoring status** — Monitored=green, Unmonitored=orange, Offline=red\n- 🔗 **Clickthrough** — click a device name to open its management interface\n- 📏 **Column widths** — Rack (60px), U (40px), IP (120px), Notes (35% wide)\n- 🔢 **Physical order** — sorted by Rack then rack unit (U)\n- ∅ **Null handling** — devices without IPs show \"-\"\n\n[Open Full Inventory →](/d/dt-rack-inventory)",
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        }
      }
    },
